      "date": "2012-01-23 15:18:34.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1:\n\nWangdi, i would call this field *_layout_gen instead, to be consistent with the LOV EA. So it seems that this patch isn't needed since you will take care of this in review 1965, right?\n\nAndreas, as for mea_dtpool_name/mea_mdpool_name, yes, i think it would be great to make the distinction. That said, i am quite confused by what's is the difference between lmv_mds_md and lmv_stripe_md?",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
